Decision Tree (Play Outside)     



                 Weather
               /   |    \
            Sunny Overcast Rain
             /        |       \
        Humidity     Play     Wind
         /    \               /   \
      High   Normal       Strong  Weak
       |        |           |       |
      No       Yes         No      Yes




Explanation of Conditions
1 Weather
Sunny
Overcast
Rain

2 If Weather = Sunny
Check Humidity
High → ❌ Don’t Play
Normal → ✅ Play

3 If Weather = Overcast
Always → ✅ Play

4 If Weather = Rain
Check Wind
Strong → ❌ Don’t Play
Weak → ✅ Play

Input → Output
Weather	      Humidity  Wind	Output
Sunny	       High	Weak	No
Sunny	       Normal	Weak	Yes
Rain	       High	Strong	No
Overcast       High	Weak	Yes

Conclusion

1 Decision Trees split data based on conditions
2 Easy to understand and visualize
3 Used for classification problems
4 Mimics human decision-making